    "166254426351b8cdff": {
      "type": "loop-article-img-txt",
      "blocks": {
        "166254426398103b88-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Specialized hearing aids",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "166254426398103b88-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You may associate hearing aids with <em>increased <\/em>sound intensity, but some devices can actually benefit sufferers of noise sensitivity anxiety by emitting a calming sound, such as running water. For some people, this can help to reduce feelings of panic, allowing them to focus on the calming sound instead of external noises.<\/p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
